  <brief_title>Insecticidal School Uniforms for Dengue Prevention in Thailand</brief_title>
  <acronym>DengueTools</acronym>
  <official_title>Can Insecticide-treated School Uniforms Reduce Dengue Infections in School-aged Children in Thailand</official_title>
